data.description: Back on the market with beautiful new renovations and a highly motivated seller! Brand new kitchen & appliances, living room wet bar, and guest bathroom countertop + fixture! Great condition private unit in a well kept gated community in the Arden/Santa Anita neighborhood This unit features 2 nicely sized bedrooms, 1.5 bath, with a beautiful wet bar in the living room. 1/2 of the windows and the water heater were replaced in June of 2022. Washer and dryer are only 1 year old and will be staying with the unit! The back patio leads out to a quiet walkway 100ft from the pool. You wont be disappointed taking a look at this fantastic property.
